Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class Item

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.Item
public final class Item extends Object
Item is a class that represents an item to be placed on the shelf It contains the type of the item and the variant of the item

The type is an enum (Ammo, Weapon, PowerUp) The variant is an int (0, 1, 2) which identifies different images of items of the same type
